.DT
broadcast_to_groups
Disk World creator help
broadcast_to_groups

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
broadcast_to_groups -  With this function you can broadcaster a message to all or some of the groups currently active.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void broadcast_to_groups(string * name,
string message)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - a string array with names of groups
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/obj/handlers/group_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

With this function you can broadcaster a message to all or
some of the groups currently active.  It will not include
your name, so make sure you identify yourself if necessary.

If "name" is empty or 0, the message will be broadcasted
to all groups.

.EP

